he video referee\", \"from\": 579, \"to\": 596}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Hay, who will also be in the final, maintains his innocence and claims he was unaware of the contact with Mills during the closing stages of the race.\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 753, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hay\", \"from\": 603, \"to\": 606}, {\"ngram\": \"his innocence\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 662}, {\"ngram\": \"the contact\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 703}, {\"ngram\": \"Mills\", \"from\": 709, \"to\": 714}, {\"ngram\": \"the closing stages\", \"from\": 722, \"to\": 740}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 744, \"to\": 752}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I do not know what happened.\", \"from\": 755, \"to\": 784, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not feel anything,' said Hay.\", \"from\": 785, \"to\": 820, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 808}, {\"ngram\": \"Hay\", \"from\": 816, \"to\": 819}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I was surprised that George came to see me after the race, because I did not feel anything, well, no more than usual.\", \"from\": 822, \"to\": 940, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"George\", \"from\": 844, \"to\": 850}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 872, \"to\": 880}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 913}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It pushed in the last 400m, it was really a massacre.\", \"from\": 942, \"to\": 996, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the last 400m\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 969}, {\"ngram\": \"a massacre\", \"from\": 985, \"to\": 995}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I turned around, there was no one left.\", \"from\": 997, \"to\": 1036, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no one\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1030}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was incredible.\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1055, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have no idea what's going to happen, it scares me.\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1108, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no idea\", \"from\": 1063, \"to\": 1070}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'For me, it happened clearly.\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1139, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's what I said to George.\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1169, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"George\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1168}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If I am guilty, sorry, but I think I was pushed.\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1218, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not think I did anything wrong, but it scares me a little bit.\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1286, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1240, \"to\": 1248}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I hope it works out and that I can get into the final.\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1343, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If the protest ever goes through and I am eliminated, of course, it will hurt but I know that I had the level to qualify and that I have never been so strong.\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1502, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the protest\", \"from\": 1347, \"to\": 1358}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 1401, \"to\": 1407}, {\"ngram\": \"the level\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1453}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For me, I am qualified, that is the most important thing.'\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1561, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most important thing\", \"from\": 1535, \"to\": 1559}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hay also reiterated that he would apologise to Mills if he felt the footage proved he was in the wrong over the collision.\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1685, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hay\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1566}, {\"ngram\": \"Mills\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 1615}, {\"ngram\": \"the footage\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1638}, {\"ngram\": \"the wrong\", \"from\": 1656, \"to\": 1665}, {\"ngram\": \"the collision\", \"from\": 1671, \"to\": 1684}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'We are at very high speeds, so of course, the slightest contact throws you off balance,' Hay said.\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1786, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"very high speeds\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1714}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1728}, {\"ngram\": \"the slightest contact\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1751}, {\"ngram\": \"balance\", \"from\": 1767, \"to\": 1774}, {\"ngram\": \"Hay\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1780}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I was pushed two years ago and I was really angry after the line.\", \"from\": 1788, \"to\": 1854, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 1853}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's what I told the others, I understand George's reaction, of course.\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 1928, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the others\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 1884}, {\"ngram\": \"George's reaction\", \"from\": 1899, \"to\": 1916}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 1927}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is the adrenaline, the disappointment.\", \"from\": 1929, \"to\": 1973, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the adrenaline\", \"from\": 1938, \"to\": 1952}, {\"ngram\": \"the disappointment\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 1972}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was very angry, he said a few sweet words to me and that it was because of me that they had fallen.\", \"from\": 1974, \"to\": 2076, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a few sweet words\", \"from\": 2001, \"to\": 2018}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'He told me: 'No, I do not care what you say'.\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2124, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I told him it was normal for him to react like that.\", \"from\": 2125, \"to\": 2177, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I told him I understood and that we would discuss it afterwards.\", \"from\": 2178, \"to\": 2242, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And that I would apologise if I am guilty, but I do not have that impression.'\", \"from\": 2243, \"to\": 2321, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that impression\", \"from\": 2304, \"to\": 2319}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When shown the footage of the incident after the race, Hay said: 'Oh yes, I am being pushed!\", \"from\": 2323, \"to\": 2415, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the footage\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2345}, {\"ngram\": \"the incident\", \"from\": 2349, \"to\": 2361}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 2368, \"to\": 2376}, {\"ngram\": \"Hay\", \"from\": 2378, \"to\": 2381}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Oh lalala!\", \"from\": 2416, \"to\": 2426, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Oh lalala\", \"from\": 2416, \"to\": 2425}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No, for me George is coming at me.'\", \"from\": 2427, \"to\": 2462, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"George\", \"from\": 2438, \"to\": 2444}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A furious Mills was asked by French media for his verdict and said: 'You know very well what happened.'\", \"from\": 2464, \"to\": 2567, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2493, \"end\": 2499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.6867226026409503, \"rank\": 0.28178040302037227, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A furious Mills\", \"from\": 2464, \"to\": 2479}, {\"ngram\": \"his verdict\", \"from\": 2510, \"to\": 2521}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 2569, \"to\": 2617, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more stories\", \"from\": 2573, \"to\": 2585}, {\"ngram\": \"our sport page\", \"from\": 2602, \"to\": 2616}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandIns